"1. Turn on Hotspot. 2. Connect the other device (client) to the hotspot. 3. On that device, modify the WiFi connection. 4. Click Advanced Options 5. Set to manual proxy: Enter Proxy Host Enter Proxy Port 6. Click Save, and you are done.
You can now enjoy the VPN connection of the host device!
[If you want the device to not sleep while tethering, stay on the app's home screen.]"
